
Veydrix DNS & Email Setup Guide (Dynadot + Zoho Mail)

A records for GitHub Pages (root):
185.199.108.153
185.199.109.153
185.199.110.153
185.199.111.153

CNAME for www -> <your-github-username>.github.io

SPF (TXT):
v=spf1 include:zoho.com ~all

DMARC (TXT) at _dmarc.veydrix.app:
v=DMARC1; p=quarantine; rua=mailto:postmaster@veydrix.app; pct=100; fo=1

DKIM: generate selector in Zoho Mail admin and add TXT record:
selector._domainkey.veydrix.app  v=DKIM1; k=rsa; p=YOUR_ZOHO_PUBLIC_KEY
